Free-listed food avoidances and aversions

A dataset containing free-listed food avoidances and aversions, the symptoms experienced if consuming aversive foods, and the perceived consequences of consuming foods that are taboo.

mysore2015food

Format

A data frame with 102 rows and 69 variables:

ID

participant ID

aversion

first item listed as pregnancy aversion

symptom

symptom experienced from first mentioned aversion

aversion2

second item listed as pregnancy aversion

symptom2

symptom experienced from second mentioned aversion

aversion3

third item listed as pregnancy aversion

symptom3

symptom experienced from third mentioned aversion

fourth item listed as pregnancy aversion

symptom experienced from fourth mentioned aversion

aversion5

fifth item listed as pregnancy aversion

symptom5

symptom experienced from fifth mentioned aversion

avoidance1

first item listed as pregnancy avoidance

learn1

how individual learned about food avoidance

consequence1

consequence of consuming forbidden item

avoidance2

how individual learned about food avoidance

consequence2

consequence of consuming forbidden item

consequence3

consequence of consuming forbidden item
